      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Counter other)
        compares one COUNTER report to the other. Allows for time-dependent ordering of COUNTER reports.
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<Counter>
        Parameters:
        other - the other COUNTER report, the actual one is compared to return int 1, if the actual report dates later than the other one and -1 if it dates earlier.

      • add

        public Counter add(Counter other)
        adds another COUNTER report to the actual one. The request fields of the other report are added to the ones of the actual report, the String fields are retained from the actual COUNTER report.
        Parameters:
        other - the other COUNTER report, the actual one is compared to
        Returns:
        Counter the updated object
